---
title: Activity Diagram - Login Pengguna
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Mulai]) --> Buka[Buka Halaman /login]
    Buka --> Input[Input Email + Password]
    Input --> Submit[Klik Tombol Sign In]
    Submit --> Validate{Format Valid?}
    Validate -->|Tidak| ShowFormErr[Tampilkan Error Form]
    ShowFormErr --> Input
    Validate -->|Ya| AuthCall[Panggil Supabase Auth]
    AuthCall --> AuthOk{Kredensial<br/>Benar?}
    AuthOk -->|Tidak| ShowAuthErr[Tampilkan 'Email/Password Salah']
    ShowAuthErr --> Input
    AuthOk -->|Ya| FetchRoles[Ambil Role + Permissions]
    FetchRoles --> StoreSession[Simpan Sesi + Permissions]
    StoreSession --> Redirect[Redirect ke /dashboard]
    Redirect --> RenderNav[Render Sidebar Sesuai Role]
    RenderNav --> End([Selesai])

    classDef startEnd fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32,color:#000
    classDef decision fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f57f17,color:#000
    classDef action fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
    classDef error fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#c62828,color:#000
    class Start,End startEnd
    class Validate,AuthOk decision
    class Buka,Input,Submit,AuthCall,FetchRoles,StoreSession,Redirect,RenderNav action
    class ShowFormErr,ShowAuthErr error
